  <h2>Share Your Knowledge and Impact the Future</h2>
  <p>
    Orbii KM is designed to provide professionals with a simple and flexible platform to share their ideas, experiences, and thoughts. Whether you want to discuss AI use cases, data analysis, cybersecurity practices, or digital strategies, you can help raise the conversation and bring real value.
  </p>
  <p>
    It’s not about hype or buzzwords, but about sharing concrete experiences, without filters, to nurture a community of professionals and push real-world practices forward.
  </p>

  <!-- Simple form for applying to become an Insight Builder -->
  <h2>Apply to Become an Insight Builder</h2>
  <p>
    Become a key player in knowledge development and join passionate experts to build bridges between the Tech, Digital, Data, AI, Cybersecurity communities, and more.
  </p>

  
  <form id="insight-builder-form" action="/send_email.php" method="POST">
    <label for="name">Full Name:</label><br>
    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required><br><br>

    <label for="email">Email:</label><br>
    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required><br><br>

    <label for="expertise">Area of Expertise:</label><br>
    <input type="text" id="expertise" name="expertise" required><br><br>

    <label for="message">Why do you want to become an Insight Builder?</label><br>
    <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea><br><br>

    <input type="submit" value="Submit">
  </form>
  


  <!-- Success Message -->
  <div class="success-message" id="success-message">
    Thank you for applying! We will review your submission and get back to you soon.
  </div>

  <!-- Error Message -->
  <div class="error-message" id="error-message">
    Oops! Something went wrong. Please try again later.
  </div>

  <script>
    document.getElementById("insight-builder-form").addEventListener("submit", function(e) {
      e.preventDefault(); // Prevent the form from submitting the default way
      
      var formData = new FormData(this); // Gather form data

      fetch('/send_email.php', {
        method: 'POST',
        body: formData
      })
      .then(response => response.text())
      .then(data => {
        // Show success message on the same page
        document.getElementById("success-message").style.display = "block";
        
        // Hide error message if it was displayed previously
        document.getElementById("error-message").style.display = "none";

        // Optionally, reset the form fields
        document.getElementById("insight-builder-form").reset();
      })
      .catch(error => {
        // Show error message
        document.getElementById("error-message").style.display = "block";
        document.getElementById("success-message").style.display = "none";
        console.error("Error:", error);
      });
    });
  </script>

{% endblock %}
